==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Retriever
<hw>Re*triev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who retrieves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A dor, or a breed of dogs,
chiefly employed to retrieve, or to find and recover game birds that
have been killed or wounded.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Retrim</ent>⟦br⟧
